Created by Jane Kang, March 11th 2014
iOS 7 required

basic functionalities
- saves a picture with title, comment
- allow user to search for picture on instagram and flickr
- allow user to take a picture with camera or pick a picture from photo album
- tweet the picture
- apply filters to picture
- crop a picture
- edit a picture after saving it
- database
- app icon

additional functionalities
- launch icon
- save, edit, delete button on the navbar
- undo enabled on filter editor
- undo all enabled on picture cropper
- tabbar icons
- add/edit/detailview images customized to the height of the view
  (if the screen is longer than usual, images extend)
- image placeholder on camera view controller
- double tap on camera view image pop the camera view controller
- resizable cropper with pinches, size reset enabled
- image savable with image placeholder, no title, no comment
- alert when user tried to tweet without logging into twitter
- clear images and search queries on re-pushing search view
- button text change color on touch